---
// CFO Dashboard — Inteligencia y Análisis Financiero
// Proyección de flujo de caja semanal basada en historial real de cierre y pago
// por cliente. Charts en CSS puro; sin librerías externas.
import AppLayout from '../../layouts/AppLayout.astro';
import { getCFO, money } from '../../lib/queries';

const D = await getCFO();
const hayDatos = D.items.length > 0;

const dsoColor = D.kpis.dso === 0 ? '#99a2af' : D.kpis.dso <= 30 ? '#059669' : D.kpis.dso <= 60 ? '#f59e0b' : '#ef4444';
const concColor = D.kpis.concentracion >= 70 ? '#ef4444' : D.kpis.concentracion >= 50 ? '#f59e0b' : '#059669';
const maxCliente = Math.max(1, ...D.rankClientes.map(c => c.valorEsperado));

// Precomputar anchos de barras (evita template literals complejos en la plantilla)
const semanasConAncho = D.semanas.map(s => ({
    ...s,
    ancho: s.valorEsperado > 0 ? Math.max(2, Math.round((s.valorEsperado / D.maxSemana) * 100)) : 0,
    subLabel: s.n > 0 ? (s.n === 1 ? '1 cotización' : s.n + ' cotizaciones') : 'sin cotizaciones',
}));
const rankClientesConAncho = D.rankClientes.map(c => ({
    ...c,
    ancho: Math.max(2, Math.round((c.valorEsperado / maxCliente) * 100)),
    tasaLabel: c.tasaPct + '%',
}));
---

<AppLayout title="Finanzas — Cord" page="cfo" heading="Finanzas">
    <slot slot="page-sub">Proyección financiera basada en historial real de cierre y cobro por cliente.</slot>
    <div slot="page-tabs">
        <a href="/app/cfo" class="ph-tab active">Finanzas</a>
        <a href="/app/analitica" class="ph-tab">Analítica</a>
    </div>

    {!hayDatos && (
        <section class="empty">
            <div class="empty-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 3v18h18"/><path d="m19 9-5 5-4-4-3 3"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h2>Sin pipeline activo</h2>
            <p>Cuando tengas cotizaciones enviadas o vistas, aquí verás la proyección de flujo de caja semana a semana basada en el historial de cada cliente.</p>
            <a href="/app/cotizaciones/nueva" class="empty-cta">+ Crear cotización</a>
        </section>
    )}

    {hayDatos && (
        <>
        <!-- KPIs financieros -->
        <section class="kpis">
            <div class="kpi">
                <span class="kpi-label">PIPELINE TOTAL</span>
                <span class="editorial kpi-num">{money(D.kpis.totalPipeline, 0)}</span>
                <span class="kpi-sub">{D.items.length} cotización{D.items.length === 1 ? '' : 'es'} activas (enviadas + vistas)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="kpi">
                <span class="kpi-label">INGRESO ESPERADO</span>
                <span class="editorial kpi-num kpi-ok">{money(D.kpis.totalEsperado, 0)}</span>
                <span class="kpi-sub">ponderado por tasa histórica de cierre por cliente</span>
            </div>
            <div class="kpi">
                <span class="kpi-label">DSO (DÍAS A COBRO)</span>
                <span class="editorial kpi-num" style={'color:' + dsoColor}>{D.kpis.dso === 0 ? '—' : D.kpis.dso}<span class="kpi-pct">{D.kpis.dso > 0 ? ' días' : ''}</span></span>
                <span class="kpi-sub">días de ventas pendientes de cobro este mes</span>
            </div>
            <div class="kpi">
                <span class="kpi-label">CONCENTRACIÓN</span>
                <span class="editorial kpi-num" style={'color:' + concColor}>{D.kpis.concentracion}<span class="kpi-pct">%</span></span>
                <span class="kpi-sub">del pipeline en {D.rankClientes[0]?.empresa ?? 'un cliente'}; riesgo de dependencia</span>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Alertas -->
        {(D.kpis.nSilenciadas > 0 || D.kpis.concentracion >= 70) && (
            <section class="alerts">
                {D.kpis.concentracion >= 70 && (
                    <div class="alert alert-warn">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 001.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 001.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 00-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg>
                        <span>Alta concentración: {D.kpis.concentracion}% del pipeline depende de <b>{D.rankClientes[0]?.empresa}</b>. Diversifica para reducir riesgo.</span>
                    </div>
                )}
                {D.kpis.nSilenciadas > 0 && (
                    <div class="alert alert-blue">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
                        <span><b>{D.kpis.nSilenciadas} cotización{D.kpis.nSilenciadas === 1 ? '' : 'es'}</b> sin respuesta hace más de 7 días. Considera hacer seguimiento.</span>
                        <a href="#silenciadas" class="alert-link">Ver →</a>
                    </div>
                )}
            </section>
        )}

        <!-- Proyección semanal de flujo de caja -->
        <section class="forecast-card">
            <div class="section-head">
                <h2>Proyección de flujo de caja</h2>
                <span class="section-note">valor esperado = monto × tasa de cierre histórica del cliente</span>
            </div>
            <div class="weeks">
                {semanasConAncho.map((s) => (
                    <div class="week-row">
                        <div class="week-meta">
                            <span class="week-label">{s.label}</span>
                            <span class="week-sub">{s.subLabel}</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="week-track">
                            <span class="week-fill" style={'width:' + s.ancho + '%'}></span>
                        </div>
                        <span class="editorial week-val">
                            {s.valorEsperado > 0 ? money(s.valorEsperado, 0) : <span class="week-zero">—</span>}
                        </span>
                    </div>
                ))}
            </div>
            <p class="forecast-note">
                La proyección usa el historial real de cada cliente: tasa de cierre (aprobadas / enviadas) y tiempo promedio de cierre y cobro. Clientes nuevos usan tasas conservadoras (25–50%).
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Pipeline por cliente (ranking) -->
        <section class="rank-card">
            <div class="section-head">
                <h2>Pipeline ponderado por cliente</h2>
                <span class="section-note">ordenado por valor esperado</span>
            </div>
            <div class="rank-header">
                <span>Cliente</span>
                <span>Pipeline</span>
                <span>Tasa hist.</span>
                <span class="col-cierre">Días a cierre</span>
                <span class="col-cobro">Días a cobro</span>
                <span>Valor esperado</span>
            </div>
            {rankClientesConAncho.map((c) => (
                <div class="rank-row">
                    <div class="rank-info">
                        <span class="rank-name">{c.empresa}</span>
                        <span class="rank-meta">{c.n} cotización{c.n === 1 ? '' : 'es'} · {c.aprobHist}/{c.totalHist} hist.</span>
                        <div class="rank-barwrap">
                            <span class="rank-bar" style={'width:' + c.ancho + '%'}></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <span class="editorial rank-amount">{money(c.totalPipeline, 0)}</span>
                    <span class:list={['tasa-pill', c.tasaPct >= 60 ? 'tasa-ok' : c.tasaPct >= 30 ? 'tasa-mid' : 'tasa-low']}>
                        {c.tasaLabel}
                    </span>
                    <span class="col-cierre days-val">{c.avgDiasCierre}d</span>
                    <span class="col-cobro days-val">{c.avgDiasCierre + c.avgDiasPago}d</span>
                    <span class="editorial rank-expected">{money(c.valorEsperado, 0)}</span>
                </div>
            ))}
        </section>

        <!-- Detalle del pipeline -->
        <section class="pipeline-card">
            <div class="section-head">
                <h2>Detalle del pipeline</h2>
                <span class="section-note">{D.items.length} cotización{D.items.length === 1 ? '' : 'es'} activas</span>
            </div>
            <div class="pipe-table">
                <div class="pipe-head">
                    <span>Folio</span>
                    <span>Cliente</span>
                    <span>Estado</span>
                    <span>Monto</span>
                    <span>Tasa</span>
                    <span>Cobro est.</span>
                    <span>Valor esp.</span>
                </div>
                {D.items.slice(0, 20).map((item) => (
                    <a href={'/app/cotizaciones/' + item.id} class="pipe-row">
                        <span class="pipe-folio">{item.folio}</span>
                        <span class="pipe-empresa">{item.empresa}</span>
                        <span class:list={['status-pill', item.status === 'viewed' ? 'sp-viewed' : 'sp-sent']}>
                            {item.status === 'viewed' ? 'Vista' : 'Enviada'}
                        </span>
                        <span class="editorial pipe-total">{money(item.total, 0)}</span>
                        <span class="pipe-tasa">{item.tasaPct}%</span>
                        <span class="pipe-dias">{item.diasParaCobro <= 0 ? 'hoy' : 'en ' + item.diasParaCobro + 'd'}</span>
                        <span class="editorial pipe-val">{money(item.valorEsperado, 0)}</span>
                    </a>
                ))}
                {D.items.length > 20 && (
                    <div class="pipe-more">+{D.items.length - 20} cotizaciones más</div>
                )}
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Cotizaciones silenciadas -->
        {D.silenciadas.length > 0 && (
            <section class="silenciadas-card" id="silenciadas">
                <div class="section-head">
                    <h2>Sin respuesta (+7 días)</h2>
                    <span class="section-note">candidatas a seguimiento</span>
                </div>
                {D.silenciadas.map((s) => (
                    <a href={'/app/cotizaciones/' + s.id} class="sil-row">
                        <span class="sil-folio">{s.folio}</span>
                        <span class="sil-empresa">{s.empresa}</span>
                        <span class="sil-dias">{s.dias} días</span>
                        <span class="editorial sil-total">{money(s.total, 0)}</span>
                        <span class="sil-action">Ver →</span>
                    </a>
                ))}
            </section>
        )}
        </>
    )}
</AppLayout>

<style>
    /* KPIs */
    .kpis {
        display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 0;
        margin-bottom: 2.4rem;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }
    .kpi { padding: 1.5rem 1.7rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; border-left: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
    .kpi:first-child { border-left: none; padding-left: 0; }
    .kpi-label { font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1.6px; color: #99a2af; }
    .kpi-num { font-size: 2rem; color: var(--color-blue-deep); line-height: 1; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
    .kpi-ok { color: #059669; }
    .kpi-pct { font-size: 1rem; }
    .kpi-sub { font-size: 0.76rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.4; }

    /* Alertas */
    .alerts { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; margin-bottom: 2.4rem; }
    .alert { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; padding: 0.9rem 1.1rem; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 0.82rem; line-height: 1.5; }
    .alert svg { width: 17px; height: 17px; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .alert b { font-weight: 700; }
    .alert-warn { background: #fefce8; border: 1px solid #fde047; color: #713f12; }
    .alert-warn svg { stroke: #ca8a04; }
    .alert-blue { background: #eff6ff; border: 1px solid #bfdbfe; color: #1e3a5f; }
    .alert-blue svg { stroke: #3b82f6; }
    .alert-link { margin-left: auto; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; white-space: nowrap; }
    .alert-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* Section header */
    .section-head { display: flex; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; padding-bottom: 0.7rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
    .section-head h2 { font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1.6px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #99a2af; margin: 0; }
    .section-note { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }

    /* Proyección semanal */
    .forecast-card { margin-bottom: 2.4rem; }
    .weeks { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .week-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 160px 1fr 150px; gap: 1rem; align-items: center; }
    .week-meta { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; }
    .week-label { font-size: 0.84rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text); }
    .week-sub { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
    .week-track { height: 12px; background: var(--color-bg-soft); border-radius: 100px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
    .week-fill { display: block; height: 100%; border-radius: 100px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1e3a5f, #10b981); min-width: 0; transition: width 0.7s var(--ease-spring); }
    .week-val { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-blue-deep); text-align: right; white-space: nowrap; }
    .week-zero { color: #c4cdd8; font-size: 0.88rem; }
    .forecast-note { font-size: 0.73rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.55; padding-top: 0.8rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); margin: 0; }

    /* Ranking de clientes */
    .rank-card { margin-bottom: 2.4rem; }
    .rank-header {
        display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 120px 80px 90px 90px 130px;
        gap: 0.75rem; padding: 0.4rem 0.6rem;
        font-size: 0.62rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #99a2af;
    }
    .rank-row {
        display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 120px 80px 90px 90px 130px;
        gap: 0.75rem; padding: 0.85rem 0.6rem; align-items: center;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }
    .rank-info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 3px; min-width: 0; }
    .rank-name { font-size: 0.84rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text); white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
    .rank-meta { font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
    .rank-barwrap { height: 5px; background: var(--color-bg-soft); border-radius: 100px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); margin-top: 4px; }
    .rank-bar { display: block; height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1e3a5f, #10b981); border-radius: 100px; }
    .rank-amount { font-size: 0.86rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
    .rank-expected { font-size: 0.92rem; color: #059669; }
    .tasa-pill { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 9px; border-radius: 100px; font-size: 0.73rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .tasa-ok { background: #dcfce7; color: #15803d; }
    .tasa-mid { background: #fef9c3; color: #a16207; }
    .tasa-low { background: #fee2e2; color: #b91c1c; }
    .days-val { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
    .col-cierre, .col-cobro { }

    /* Tabla de pipeline */
    .pipeline-card { margin-bottom: 2.4rem; }
    .pipe-table { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
    .pipe-head {
        display: grid; grid-template-columns: 90px 1.4fr 80px 110px 60px 80px 110px;
        gap: 0.7rem; padding: 0.4rem 0.6rem;
        font-size: 0.62rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #99a2af;
    }
    .pipe-row {
        display: grid; grid-template-columns: 90px 1.4fr 80px 110px 60px 80px 110px;
        gap: 0.7rem; padding: 0.8rem 0.6rem; align-items: center;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        text-decoration: none; color: inherit; transition: background 0.18s;
    }
    .pipe-row:hover { background: #f8f9fb; border-radius: 8px; }
    .pipe-folio { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-family: 'SF Mono', ui-monospace, monospace; }
    .pipe-empresa { font-size: 0.84rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-text); white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
    .pipe-total { font-size: 0.86rem; color: var(--color-text); }
    .pipe-tasa { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
    .pipe-dias { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
    .pipe-val { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #059669; }
    .pipe-more { padding: 0.9rem 0.6rem; font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); }

    /* Status pills (reutiliza .status-pill del layout) */
    .sp-viewed { background: #fef9c3; color: #a16207; }
    .sp-sent { background: #dbeafe; color: #1d4ed8; }

    /* Silenciadas */
    .silenciadas-card { margin-bottom: 2.4rem; }
    .sil-row {
        display: grid; grid-template-columns: 90px 1fr 80px 120px 60px;
        gap: 0.7rem; padding: 0.8rem 0.6rem; align-items: center;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        text-decoration: none; color: inherit; transition: background 0.18s;
    }
    .sil-row:hover { background: #f8f9fb; border-radius: 8px; }
    .sil-folio { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-family: 'SF Mono', ui-monospace, monospace; }
    .sil-empresa { font-size: 0.84rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-text); }
    .sil-dias { font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-warn); }
    .sil-total { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--color-text); }
    .sil-action { font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-blue-deep); }

    /* Empty state */
    .empty { padding: 5rem 2rem; text-align: center; }
    .empty-icon { width: 52px; height: 52px; margin: 0 auto 1.4rem; color: #c4cdd8; }
    .empty-icon svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; }
    .empty h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 0.5rem; }
    .empty p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 460px; margin: 0 auto 1.4rem; line-height: 1.6; }
    .empty-cta { display: inline-block; background: var(--color-blue-deep); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.86rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 11px 20px; border-radius: 10px; }

    @media (max-width: 1100px) {
        .kpis { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
        .kpi:nth-child(odd) { border-left: none; padding-left: 0; }
        .kpi:nth-child(3), .kpi:nth-child(4) { border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
        .rank-header, .rank-row { grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 110px 70px 130px; }
        .col-cierre, .col-cobro { display: none; }
        .pipe-head, .pipe-row { grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr 75px 100px 90px; }
        .pipe-tasa { display: none; }
        .sil-row { grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr 70px 110px 50px; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 720px) {
        .kpis { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
        .week-row { grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr 110px; }
        .rank-header { display: none; }
        .rank-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr 90px 70px; }
        .rank-expected { display: none; }
        .pipe-head { display: none; }
        .pipe-row { grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr 90px; }
        .pipe-total, .pipe-dias, .pipe-val { display: none; }
        .pipe-val { display: block; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 500px) {
        .kpis { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .kpi { border-left: none; padding-left: 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
        .kpi:first-child { border-top: none; }
        .week-row { grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr 100px; }
    }
</style>
